  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《About》</h2>《Moirs》is a 7 Keys rhythm game, step into the world of music and enjoy the journey!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336460/extras/91687dc161ca56eb8324df85d95d8d86.poster.avif?t=1595169565\" width=494 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336460/extras/91687dc161ca56eb8324df85d95d8d86.webm?t=1595169565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336460/extras/91687dc161ca56eb8324df85d95d8d86.mp4?t=1595169565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Features》</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  3+4 Keys, Sky notes and Ground notes test your hand-eye coordination.<br></li><li>  7 original songs with their respective, elaborate background visuals.<br></li><li>  4 kinds of difficulty, having a relaxing or challenging game play.<br></li><li>  As songs unlock, the story of a girl chasing her music dream unfolds, and your game play decides the ending.<br></li><li>  Development diary and mini-game with lots of memes (?)</li></ul>",
